  <entry>
    <title>操作系统真相还原（1） -- 编写 MBR 主引导记录</title>
    <link href="/2024/07/15/kanaos2/"/>
    <url>/2024/07/15/kanaos2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="操作系统真相还原（1）-–-编写-MBR-主引导记录"><a href="#操作系统真相还原（1）-–-编写-MBR-主引导记录" class="headerlink" title="操作系统真相还原（1） – 编写 MBR 主引导记录"></a>操作系统真相还原（1） – 编写 MBR 主引导记录</h1><p>坦率的讲，我们的操作系统的运行，如同火箭升天一般，是一级一级完成的，操作系统也是这样：一级程序要完成自己任务，结束之后把权力交给下一级继续运行，随着权力的移交，执行的程序越来越复杂，最终运行起整个操作系统。BIOS就是这艘火箭的第一级，我们的故事也从这里开始。</p><h2 id="BIOS"><a href="#BIOS" class="headerlink" title="BIOS"></a>BIOS</h2><p>首先来看这张表：</p><p><img src="/../img/kanaos2/image.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>应该说，这是我们程序编写的参考。这是实模式下 1MB 内存。实模式内存就是1MB，这1MB究竟怎么分已经规定的清清楚楚。</p><p>我们开机之后，硬件写好的 BIOS 会自动启动，运行硬件检查等等的操作，最后将指令跳转到内存的0x7c00处，开始运行MBR。</p><p>BIOS怎么找到MBR？其实MBR的位置和大小是固定的，就是0盘0道1扇区（也是硬盘的第一扇区）这512字节。BIOS完成自己的任务就会将MBR加载到内存的0x7c00开始执行MBR。</p><h2 id="MBR"><a href="#MBR" class="headerlink" title="MBR"></a>MBR</h2><p>我们的MBR只有短短的512字节，它能完成的任务显然少只有少，其实它主要是把任务顺利的交给下一棒就可以了。</p><p>还是看这个最简单的MBR程序：</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-comment">; 死循环</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> $<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">; 保证刚好512字节，不足的补0</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">times</span> <span class="hljs-number">510</span> - ($ - $$) <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <br><br><span class="hljs-comment">; 最后两个字节一定是55 aa，这是约定</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xaa</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个程序什么都没有做，我们需要让它完成一些任务 ——</p><ul><li>1:输出一些信息</li><li>2:找到下一棒并把运行权力交给它</li></ul><h3 id="输出一些信息"><a href="#输出一些信息" class="headerlink" title="输出一些信息"></a>输出一些信息</h3><p>在输出上，我倾向于将它写成类似函数的样子，方便我们以后还可能使用，这两个函数我们都会放在print.asm文件里完成。</p><p>第一，我们先做个清屏函数；</p><p>原理：<br>    0x10中断的0x06功能，上卷全部行。<br>    AH 功能号&#x3D; 0x06，AL &#x3D; 上卷的行数(如果为 0,表示全部)，BH &#x3D; 上卷行颜色属性<br>    (CL,CH) &#x3D; 窗口左上角的(X,Y)位置<br>    (DL,DH) &#x3D; 窗口右下角的(X,Y)位置<br>    无返回值；</p><p>实现：</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-comment">; 清屏函数</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">clear:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">pusha</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x0600</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x0700</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x184f</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x10</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">popa</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">ret</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二，我们实现输出；</p><p>原理：<br>    向显存中的显示字符显示区域直接输出内容，会直接被显示出来</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-comment">; 打印函数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; ax 存储显存的位置</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; bx 存储打印内容的地址，打印到第一个&#x27;\0&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; cx 存储颜色信息</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; dx 存储打印的偏离字数</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">print:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">pusha</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">gs</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ss</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">si</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">print_char:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>, [<span class="hljs-built_in">ss</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>+<span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>]<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">cmp</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">je</span> print_end<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">add</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">shl</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">byte</span> [<span class="hljs-built_in">gs</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>],<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">byte</span> [<span class="hljs-built_in">gs</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>],<span class="hljs-built_in">cl</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">shr</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">inc</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">si</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> print_char<br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">print_end:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">popa</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">ret</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们只需要在主文件里<code>%include &quot;source/print.asm&quot;</code>，然后调用这两个函数就可以了。这是我们的主文件</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-meta">SECTION</span> MBR vstart=<span class="hljs-number">0x7c00</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">init:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">cs</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ds</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ss</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">es</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">fs</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">sp</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x7c00</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> clear<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xb800</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,program_begin<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cl</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x07</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x0</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> print<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,mbr_begin<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">80</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> print<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> $<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">%include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;source/print.asm&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">program_begin:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;program begin!&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">mbr_begin:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;mbr begin!&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">times</span> <span class="hljs-number">510</span> - ($ - $$) <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <br><span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xaa</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样boot.asm和print.asm存储在source文件夹中。</p><p>我们可以看一下效果：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">nasm source/boot.asm -o boot.bin<br>dd if=boot.bin of=hd60M.img bs=512 count=1 conv=notrunc<br>bochs -f bochsrc.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../img/kanaos2/image-1.png" alt="alt text"></p><h3 id="找到下一棒并把运行权力交给它"><a href="#找到下一棒并把运行权力交给它" class="headerlink" title="找到下一棒并把运行权力交给它"></a>找到下一棒并把运行权力交给它</h3><p>事实上，我们首先要解决的是读硬盘。mbr程序是写在固定地方的，但是接下来的程序并不是。<br>所以我们需要判断接下来的程序在哪里，将其读入内存，再将程序跳转到刚刚读入的新程序，就完成了整个MBR的交接任务。</p><p>我们先用函数编写读磁盘的过程。</p><p>原理：and al,0x0f<br>    读取的扇区数写入端口 0x1f2<br>    LBA 地址存入端口 0x1f3 ~ 0x1f6<br>    向 0x1f6 的Device设置 lba 第 24~27 位，写为 1110<br>    向 0x1f7 端口写入读命令,0x20<br>    向 0x1f7 端口使用读命令，检测硬盘状态，第4位为1表示硬盘控制器已准备好数据传输，第7位为1表示硬盘忙<br>    最后从 0x1f0 端口读数据</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-comment">; 实模式下的读磁盘函数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; eax -- 起始扇区 lba 地址</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; bx  -- 写入的地址</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">; cx  -- 待读入的扇区数</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">rd_disk_16:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">pusha</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">esi</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">di</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">cx</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f2</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">cl</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">esi</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f3</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">shr</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f4</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">shr</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f5</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">shr</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x0f</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">or</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xe0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f6</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x20</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f7</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">al</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">rd_disk_16_not_ready:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">nop</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x88</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">cmp</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">al</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x08</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">jnz</span> rd_disk_16_not_ready<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">di</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">256</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mul</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cx</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0x1f0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">rd_disk_16_read:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> [<span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>],<span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">add</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">loop</span> rd_disk_16_read<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">popa</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">ret</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样主函数加上：</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">eax</span>,LOADER_START_SECTOR<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,LOADER_BASE_ADDR<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cx</span>,LOADER_SECTOR_NUM<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> rd_disk_16<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> LOADER_BASE_ADDR<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>加上loader.asm和setting</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-meta">%include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;source/setting&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">section</span> loader vstart=LOADER_BASE_ADDR<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ax</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xb800</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bx</span>,loader_begin<br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cl</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xa4</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">dx</span>,<span class="hljs-number">160</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> print<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> $<br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">loader_begin:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;loader begin!&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">%include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;source/print.asm&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm">LOADER_BASE_ADDR <span class="hljs-built_in">equ</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x900</span><br>LOADER_START_SECTOR <span class="hljs-built_in">equ</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x2</span><br>LOADER_SECTOR_NUM <span class="hljs-built_in">equ</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x1</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>就可以运行了。</p><p>我们的编译脚本也更换一下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">if nasm source/boot.asm -o boot.bin<br>then<br>    if nasm source/loader.asm -o loader.bin<br>    then<br>        dd if=boot.bin of=hd60M.img bs=512 count=1 conv=notrunc<br>        dd if=loader.bin of=hd60M.img bs=512 count=2 seek=2 conv=notrunc<br>        bochs -f bochsrc.txt<br>    else<br>        echo &#x27;编译失败&#x27;<br>    fi<br>else<br>    echo &#x27;编译失败&#x27;<br>fi<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
