  <entry>
    <title>操作系统真相还原（0） -- 环境配置</title>
    <link href="/2024/07/15/kanaos1/"/>
    <url>/2024/07/15/kanaos1/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="操作系统真相还原（0）-–-环境配置"><a href="#操作系统真相还原（0）-–-环境配置" class="headerlink" title="操作系统真相还原（0） – 环境配置"></a>操作系统真相还原（0） – 环境配置</h1><p>原书是在windows上使用linux虚拟机，在虚拟机里使用bochs再开虚拟机实现的。我们就不这么复杂了。我会直接实机使用linux，使用bochs和qemu进行实验。先给出我的linux配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">OS: Fedora Linux 40 (Workstation Edition) x86_64 <br>Kernel: 6.8.5-301.fc40.x86_64<br>DE: GNOME 46.3.1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="nasm-与-bochs-安装"><a href="#nasm-与-bochs-安装" class="headerlink" title="nasm 与 bochs 安装"></a>nasm 与 bochs 安装</h2><p>fedora的软件库是很新的，原谅我就不去编译源代码了，所以我就直接使用包管理器来下载了。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">事实上我还用 dnf 顺便下载了 bochs-debugger  bochs-gdb  bochs-devel</span><br>sudo dnf install nasm bochs<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">我安装的版本</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">NASM version 2.16.01 compiled on Jan 25 2024</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">Bochs x86 Emulator 2.8 Built from GitHub snapshot on March 10, 2024</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="bochs使用"><a href="#bochs使用" class="headerlink" title="bochs使用"></a>bochs使用</h2><p>首先使用bximage指令创建虚拟硬盘。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">创建记录</span><br><br>bximage <br><br>========================================================================<br>                                bximage<br>  Disk Image Creation / Conversion / Resize and Commit Tool for Bochs<br>                                  $Id$<br>========================================================================<br><br>1. Create new floppy or hard disk image<br>2. Convert hard disk image to other format (mode)<br>3. Resize hard disk image<br>4. Commit &#x27;undoable&#x27; redolog to base image<br>5. Disk image info<br><br>0. Quit<br><br>Please choose one [0] 1<br><br>Create image<br><br>Do you want to create a floppy disk image or a hard disk image?<br>Please type hd or fd. [hd] <br><br>What kind of image should I create?<br>Please type flat, sparse, growing, vpc or vmware4. [flat] <br><br>Choose the size of hard disk sectors.<br>Please type 512, 1024 or 4096. [512] <br><br>Enter the hard disk size in megabytes, between 10 and 8257535<br>[10] 60<br><br>What should be the name of the image?<br>[c.img] hd60M.img<br><br>Creating hard disk image &#x27;hd60M.img&#x27; with CHS=121/16/63 (sector size = 512)<br><br>The following line should appear in your bochsrc:<br>  ata0-master: type=disk, path=&quot;hd60M.img&quot;, mode=flat<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再编写 bochsrc.txt 配置文件</p><ul><li>bochsrc.txt <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">megs : 512<br><br>romimage: file=/usr/share/bochs/BIOS-bochs-latest<br>vgaromimage: file=/usr/share/bochs/VGABIOS-lgpl-latest<br><br>boot: disk<br>log: bochs.out<br><br>mouse:enabled=0<br>keyboard:keymap=/usr/share/bochs/keymaps/x11-pc-us.map<br><br>ata0:enabled=1,ioaddr1=0x1f0,ioaddr2=0x3f0,irq=14<br><br>ata0-master: type=disk, path=&quot;hd60M.img&quot;, mode=flat,cylinders=121,heads=16,spt=63<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>我们编写一个最简单的汇编程序来测试一下。</p><ul><li>boot.asm<figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> $<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">times</span> <span class="hljs-number">510</span> - ($ - $$) <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <br><span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0xaa</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>用脚本直接进行编译运行：</p><ul><li>build.asm<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">nasm -o boot.bin boot.asm<br><br>dd if=boot.bin of=hd60M.img bs=512 count=1 conv=notrunc<br><br>bochs -f bochsrc.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>可以看到，虽然界面只是基本开始界面，但不会报错了。测试成功！</p><h2 id="gcc降级"><a href="#gcc降级" class="headerlink" title="gcc降级"></a>gcc降级</h2><p>在编译一些书里面的内容的时候，我们是不能使用当前的gcc版本的。我们要解决这个问题。</p><p>首先，我是不愿意在我的fedora实机上作gcc降级的，我的日常学习就是在实机上，毕竟在一般情况下我不会使用一个10多年前的gcc，原书使用的是gcc4.6.2，但是我当前的版本是14.1.1。在当前这个时间点去编译安装10多年前的一个gcc版本其实有点麻烦，甚至说都存在C里语法结构的修改导致当前版本编译器都编译不了这个老版本。</p><p>我们就使用docker使用容器的方法来解决这个矛盾好了，我们使用docker使用gcc4.4的版本。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">dokcer 配置</span><br>sudo usermod -aG docker $USER<br>sudo chmod 777 /var/run/docker.sock<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">我们用ubuntu来搭建老版本的gcc</span><br>docker pull ubuntu<br>docker run -it --name &#x27;oldgcc&#x27;  --hostname &#x27;oldgcc&#x27; -v /home/wang/Aprogram/KanaOs/share:/share:Z ubuntu  /bin/bash<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">创建后关闭之后再使用</span><br>docker start oldgcc<br>docker attach oldgcc<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">管理容器</span><br>docker ps -a<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">接下来是在ubuntu docker下运行</span><br>apt-get update<br>apt-get install nano<br>nano /etc/apt/sources.list<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">写入</span><br>deb http://dk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ trusty main universe<br>deb http://dk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ trusty-updates main universe<br><br>apt-get update<br>报错，GPG error缺少公钥，我们直接导入<br><br>apt install gnupg -y<br><br>apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys xxx缺少的公钥<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">再更新</span><br>apt-get update<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">下载安装</span><br>apt-get install gcc-4.4 -y<br>apt-get install g++-4.4 -y<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">检查</span><br>gcc-4.4 --version<br><br>我的版本：gcc-4.4 (Ubuntu/Linaro 4.4.7-8ubuntu1) 4.4.7<br><br>g++-4.4 --version<br><br>我的版本：g++-4.4 (Ubuntu/Linaro 4.4.7-8ubuntu1) 4.4.7<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样我们就在docker里进行一部分编译了，同时使用share文件夹进行文件的传输。</p>]]></content>
    
    
